    <h1>NiceTuner Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="update-date">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>NiceTuner is a musical instrument tuning application. We respect your privacy, and this policy explains how we handle your data.</p>

    <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
    <p><strong>Microphone Access:</strong> The app uses the microphone solely for real-time pitch detection of musical instruments. Audio data is processed entirely on your device and <strong>is not uploaded, stored, or shared with any third party</strong>.</p>

    <h2>3. Local Storage</h2>
    <p>The app stores the following preference settings locally on your device:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Reference pitch settings</li>
        <li>Theme preferences (dark/light mode)</li>
        <li>Language settings</li>
        <li>Other tuning-related parameters</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is stored only on your device and is not transmitted to any server.</p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This app does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since all data is processed and stored locally, your data security depends entirely on the security measures of your device.</p>

    <h2>6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>
    <p>This app is not intended for children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>7. Policy Changes</h2>
    <p>If we update this privacy policy, the updated version will be published on this page.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions related to privacy, please contact us at:
        <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">aixce1024@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
